{"tid":1741980,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"姦淫擄掠聯合國","createTime":"2019-11-20T14:44:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T14:44:16.000Z","uid":49359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"31d7c1333f64e0fe1ab45b07686b6b723058009b","tid":1741980,"uid":49359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T14:44:16.000Z","msg":"聯合國性侵醜聞<br />\n過去十五年，聯合國維持和平部隊的性侵指控多達1700宗。為何聯合國設法制止事件重演，但性虐待和性剝削的問題仍然存在呢？為何至今只有53個維和部隊人員因性侵入獄？本片探討聯合國的失策和局限性，分析成員國在當中的角色。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rthk.hk/tv/dtt31/programme/31seetheworld/episode/535916\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rthk.hk%2Ftv%2Fdtt31%2Fprogramme%2F31seetheworld%2Fepisode%2F535916&d=Cf%2BepIHKvYs8nB0OclbNLEcTp%2BQsjpNju1TtMRGBB4E%3D&h=99635a6b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.rthk.hk/tv/dtt31/programme/31seetheworld/episode/535916</a>"}]}